```mermaid
classDiagram
    direction TB

    class PresentationLayer {
        <<Package>>
        API Endpoints
        Services
        +resgisterUser()
        +createPlace()
        +submitReview()
        +fetchPlaces()
    }

    class BusinessLogicLayer {
    <<Package>>
    User
    Place
    Review
    Amenity
    +validateData()
    +processRequest()
    }

    class PersistenceLayer {
    <<Package>>
    Database
    +save()
    +update()
    +delete()
    +query()
    }
    PresentationLayer --> BusinessLogicLayer : Uses Facade
    BusinessLogicLayer --> PersistenceLayer : Database Operations
```